name: App Popularity
shortDescription: App Popularity helps you track the popularity of any apps available in BigBoss - the most popular Cydia repository. These can be either your apps, or competitors, or any others you care about. App Popularity gives you the current stats and the previous from the last refresh informing you about the popularity increase. These are the same stats available in Cydia, except the fact, that you don't have to 1. wait for Cydia to load and reload it's data and accept or ignore update suggestions 2. find your app in the list of thousands of applications, wait till every next component loads and rich stats by scrolling dozens of commercials
author: Chris
